# Xplorer Update Manager

Centralized Klipper configuration repository for Formbot Xplorer 3D printers, integrated with Mainsail's Update Manager. No build system — this is a pure configuration/asset repo.

## Folder Map

| Folder | Contents |
|--------|----------|
| `01_Default_CFG/` | Modular Klipper cfg fragments and variant entry files |
| `02_Printer_cfg/` | Complete printer bundles (one file per variant+revision) |
| `03_MODs/` | Formbot official modifications |
| `04_Slicer_Profiles/` | OrcaSlicer profiles |
| `05_STEP_FILES/` | CAD parts (V1.0, V1.1) |
| `06_Manual/` | Printer manuals |
| `07_Mainsail_Settings/` | Mainsail UI JSON backups |
| `.7_XP_modules/` | Python Klipper extras (calibration) |
| `.8_Scripts/` | Shell scripts (resonance, PLR, setup) |
| `.9_MCU_Flash/` | MCU flashing scripts and Klipper .config files |

## Hardware Variants

- **V1.0**: SINGLE, IDEX, 2xGANTRY
- **V1.1**: SINGLE, IDEX, 2xGANTRY, IQEX (4-tool)

## Naming Conventions

- Config fragments: `Xp_<Function>.cfg` (e.g. `Xp_Tool0.cfg`, `Xp_Z_Axis.cfg`)
- V1.1 fragments: `Xp_V1.1_<Function>.cfg`
- Variant entry files: `Xplorer_<VARIANT>.cfg` / `Xplorer_V1.1_<VARIANT>.cfg`
- Scripts: descriptive name with tool/axis suffix (e.g. `resonances_X_t0.sh`)
- Backups: dot-prefixed (`.variables.cfg.bak`)

## Target System

Printer runs on a BTT CB2 (armbian). Key paths on the printer:
- `/home/biqu/printer_data/config/` — Klipper config root
- `/home/biqu/klipper/` — Klipper installation
- `/tmp/` — temporary resonance CSV data

